===卡特球===
李維拉的特色球種－[[切球|卡特球]]，他的球種結合了[[二縫線快速球|二縫線快速球]]和[[四縫線快速球|四縫線快速球]]，他這三種球種的速度介於90到93MPH。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/y2007/gd.html?2007_09_17_balmlb_nyamlb_1 |title=Gameday 2007 |access-date=2008-07-19 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805165542/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/y2007/gd.html?2007_09_17_balmlb_nyamlb_1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>關於到他卡特球的源由，李維拉於《The Bergen Record》當中解釋到，當他與[[拉米羅·門多薩|拉米羅·門多薩]]練習投球時，意外發現了卡特球。他告訴了[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]：「這是來自於神的，我沒有做任何事，它是自然的」<ref>{{cite news | url = http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/features/cover/news/2000/03/22/out_at_home/ | title = The Yankees allowed the Red Sox their day of Fenway glory, then dispatched Boston to resume their inexorable march back to the World Series | publisher = Sports Illustrated | author = Verducci, Tom | date = 2000-03-22 | accessdate = 2007-05-27 | archive-date = 2008-10-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081012183647/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/features/cover/news/2000/03/22/out_at_home | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[紐約日報|紐約日報]]的T.J. 奎因說到李維拉的卡特球是在1996年當佈局投手時，從約翰·維特蘭中學到的<ref>Quinn. ''New York Daily News''. 9 June 2002.</ref>。李維拉的卡特球讓大聯盟打者心生畏懼<ref name="usatoday" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/columns/stark_jayson/1382666.html |title=The pitches that scare major leaguers |publisher=ESPN |author=Stark, Jayson |accessdate=2006-08-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060630003237/http://espn.go.com/mlb/columns/stark_jayson/1382666.html |archivedate=2006-06-30 }}</ref>，如[[奇伯·瓊斯|奇伯·瓊斯]]就比喻到那是個「圓鋸」<ref>{{cite news | title = Authors take on Ruthian legends | url = http://www.signonsandiego.com/uniontrib/20060308/news_lz1s8galry.html | publisher = The San Diego Union-Tribune | date = March 8, 2006 | accessdate = 2006-08-10 | archive-date = 2008-07-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080724210106/http://www.signonsandiego.com/uniontrib/20060308/news_lz1s8galry.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>（因為對於左打者的進壘會有驟變的效果）；[[吉姆·湯米|吉姆·湯米]]也說到那是：「最好的單一球種」<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2006/07/17/sports/baseball/17curry.html | title = End in Sight, Guillén Shows Respect With a Rare Retreat | author = Curry, Jack | publisher = The New York Times | date = 2006-07-17 | accessdate = 2006-08-10 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309055821/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/07/17/sports/baseball/17curry.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>
。[[ESPN|ESPN]]的[[歐恩尼·巴基特|歐恩尼·巴基特]]談到李維拉的卡特球是「最有統治性的球種」<ref>{{cite news | url = http://insider.espn.go.com/espn/blog/index?name=olney_buster#20060929 | title = 20 best postseason weapons | author = Buster Olney | publisher = [[ESPN|ESPN]] | date = 2006-09-29 | accessdate = 2006-09-29 }} (preview only)</ref>。雖然左右開弓打者面對右投手通常都是站於左打區，較容易知道放球點，但許多左右開弓打者面對李維拉時，會選右打區來避免被卡特球凍結住。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2004/03/23/sports/baseball/23YANK.html?ex=1185508800&en=4b0b15b676654a56&ei=5070 | title = For Yankees and Rivera, It's Case Closed | publisher = The New York Times | author = Kepner, Tyler | date = 2004-03-23 | accessdate = 2007-07-25 | archive-date = 2009-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090417071146/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/03/23/sports/baseball/23YANK.html?ex=1185508800&en=4b0b15b676654a56&ei=5070 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1208/is_27_229/ai_n14713597 |title=AL East |publisher=Sporting News |date=2005-07-08 |accessdate=2007-08-23 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120710054019/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1208/is_27_229/ai_n14713597/ |archivedate=2012-07-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

=== 傳奇 ===
王牌救援投手（終結者）這個位置上場時機往往不太穩定，但李维拉在這個角色表現的令人不注意也難。他在王牌救援投手（終結者）的發揮成為了穩定，亮眼表演的代表人物。很多人讚賞李维拉的謙虛，慷慨和好心<ref name="usatoday" /><ref name="verducci" /><ref name="cyyoung" />，這些性格很難在超級明星運動員找到。當投的不好時，李維拉總是對他的演出負責。一旦他退休，大部分[[体育运动|體育]][[記者|記者]]和[[棒球|棒球]]專家預料李维拉會在符合資格的第一年就被選進[[棒球名人堂|棒球名人堂]]。<ref name="verducci" /><ref name="cutterabove" /><ref name="cyyoung" /> 而最後也不負眾望以100%得票率在符合資格的第一年進入棒球名人堂。

